University 7 is a full-stack academic administration-developed system.
The project integrates a PostgreSQL relational database, an Express.js backend, and a TailwindCSS-driven frontend.
The system manages students, instructors, courses, semesters, sections, payments, grades, and financial accounts. 
The goal is to simulate a university environment while demonstrating normalization, ACID transactions, database
triggers, REST API design, and query-based reporting.
